sum((-1)^k*binomial(n,k),'k)$HYPGEOM --> 0?

-- Example 8.1.1.
sum(binomial(3*k+1,k)*binomial(3*(n-k),n-k)/(3*k+1), 'k)$HYPGEOM

-- Dixon
sum((-1)^k*binomial(2*n,k)^3,'k)
sum((-1)^k*binomial(2*n,k)^3,'k)$HYPGEOM
